data.description: Be in the middle of exciting River Arts District events and attractions while enjoying privacy, luxury and comfort in Skypoint, one of Tampa's  iconic much-sought-after high-rise residences! Floor to ceiling windows offer abundant natural light and gorgeous views of the Hillsborough River, Riverwalk, Bucs Stadium, Straz Center, Tampa Heights and beyond! Private balcony affords amazing views of sunsets, rays of sunrise, blue sky and the city's north and northwest sights. You'll love the large bright living area; sleek contemporary kitchen with breakfast nook, rich wood cabinets and stainless steel appliances; and the bedroom with great views, walk-in closet, en suite bathroom, and laundry closet. Enjoy maintenance-free living with Skypoint amenities! Grand lobby with lounge area, 24/7 concierge to assist with deliveries, guests, etc.; resort-style heated pool and spa with gas grills and wet bar for poolside entertaining; landscaped terrace with sofas, fire pits and cozy areas for outdoor lounging; club house with floor to ceiling glass walls affording panoramic views of the city, billiard area, televisions, kitchen area, theater room and state-of-the-art fitness center. With Skypoint's ideal location directly opposite Curtis Hixon Park and Glazer Museum, the walkability score is high, supporting a healthy lifestyle. You're just a few steps to the popular Riverwalk, Straz Center, Tampa Theatre, Tampa Museum of Art and an array of great restaurants, bars, theaters and other museums. Walk to the new Water Street development, Sparksman Wharf, Amalie Arena, University of Tampa, Bayshore Drive and other Tampa attractions. And you have carless options! Water taxi, bike, scooter, and the free Trolley. Skypoint offers you urban living at its finest, schedule a showing now!  Furniture is Optional and can be negotiated.
